project.title: Taylor Cochran Music
project.description_short: Taylor Cochran is a singer/songwriter from Nashville, Tennessee who started pursuing his songwriting career in early 2013. Through his music, he aspires to send a message of joy, hope, and love.
description_long: Taylor Cochran is a singer/songwriter from Nashville, Tennessee who pursued his songwriting career in early 2013 by gaining experience playing in local bars, venues, and with his church. Through his music, he aspires to send a message of joy, hope, and love.

Adam designed and managed Taylor's website from late 2013 to mid 2014. The website was launched alongside the success of Taylor's debut EP Kickstarter campaign for which he also helped produce the promo video.
